Msg468=Only the snakes you kill by hitting with the club count towards points, the one with the most points at the end wins.
Msg469=Your team can achieve victory in two ways: steal all the cargo from the opposing team's hold and bring it to your hold to win, or alternatively, they must eliminate the opposing ship's Captain.
