[QUEST1]
Nombre=Final Rest
Desc=I buried 13 children, 13 times I had to go to that place, but you have only one chance to get out alive on this mission, the cursed tombs are near the mausoleum of the Nix Cemetery
DescFinal=Today the Cemetery is calmer thanks to your strength. Take this noble adventurer, all the people of Nix thank you.
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=13
PosMap=4
DescAudio=1048
DescFinalAudio=1049

[QUEST2]
Nombre=First steps in alchemy
Desc=Young worker, I need you to take this recipe that I gave you to my friend Caelum, so that she can teach you what you want to learn!
DescFinal=Good Luck!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=6
DescAudio=1050
DescFinalAudio=1051

[QUEST4]
Nombre=Mortal poison
Desc=I see that you have plenty of courage but you will need more than that to survive in these lands. You must have on hand all kinds of potions for the adventure. Kill 10 snakes and bring me their venom, I think I will be able to make a few antidotes for you.
DescFinal=Good job, wait for me for a moment...
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=1
PosMap=44
DescAudio=1052
DescFinalAudio=1053

[QUEST5]
Nombre=Your first hunt
Desc=Wild Wolves prowl our lands under the shadow of a sick moon. Weapons Master Bertram summons you: you must not only hunt them, but also pluck from one of them its cursed fang. Only a wolf, touched by darkness, bears it. Seek, wait... and listen for the distinct howl. The Wolf's Fang is not earned by luck, but by determination. Once you achieve it, visit me at Nix's Smithy.
DescFinal=Adventurer... You've done it! That fang doesn't come without courage. Talk to me again, I have a task for you.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=15
DescAudio=1054
DescFinalAudio=1055

[QUEST7]
Nombre=Recipes for potions
Desc=Let's test if this really works, I need a rooster feather to be able to write down my recipes. Better bring me several just in case.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=4
PosMap=218
DescAudio=1056

[QUEST11]
Nombre=Anger of the dwarf
Desc=I'm already tired of these damn orcs, they have decimated my cattle. Is this his forest? I don't care. They and those short creatures... They must be annihilated! We good citizens of Ullathorpe must regain control of the area. Go and kill five of each. Also bring me the axes of those orcs, they will be useful to me.
DescFinal=That's nice! In the same way I miss my cow, have this reward.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=16
PosMap=39
DescAudio=1057
DescFinalAudio=1058

[QUEST13]
Nombre=Eye for eye, dagger dagger
Desc=Apparently the brotherhood of criminals has not liked the massacre we have carried out with the band of outlaws who sow terror on the roads. Possibly they are from the same clan and come seeking revenge. They are not playing, they have already shed innocent blood. They have been murdering several of the city's loggers. Go and teach them that this city will not give in to their threats.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=17
PosMap=1
DescAudio=1059

[QUEST14]
Nombre=Too many wolves!
Desc=I am tired of these damned wolves terrorizing our merchants and citizens, help our hunters eliminate the Wild Wolves that stalk our forests and help Ullathorpe sleep more peacefully, I promise to give you a good reward.
DescFinal=The citizens of Ullathorpe thank you!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=9
PosMap=11
DescAudio=1060
DescFinalAudio=1061

[QUEST15]
Nombre=Combat supplies
Desc=I need shields for my crew. I have heard that turtles live near these forests, their shells would be useful to me...
DescFinal=Have your reward!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=11
PosMap=36
DescAudio=1062
DescFinalAudio=1063

[QUEST16]
Nombre=The great scam
Desc=Ullathorpe was known for her tranquility, now not even that. A plague of bandits prowls the road here and assaults the caravans that circulate between this city and the King's Castle. Kill them. Money is not interesting, I will give it to you. What's more, you can keep the loot they have.
DescFinal=How good these heads will look in the city square. Thank you.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=13
PosMap=270
DescAudio=1064
DescFinalAudio=1065

[QUEST17]
Nombre=Between shadow and wound
Desc=Pay attention. The true bandit doesn't rely on strength, but on timing. In the Elven Forest, you'll have to move among creatures that can't be stopped by paralysis, learning to observe, attack, and disappear before you can be reached. Then you'll travel to New Hope, where the fairies punish recklessness with their dark magic and every mistake is costly. There, you must remain calm and maintain control in combat. If you master stealth in both places, you'll understand how to leave an opponent defenseless with the Disabling Strike.
DescFinal=You knew how to move unseen where the enemy couldn't be stopped and maintain control where others were immobilized. Now you understand that incapacitation isn't about strength: it's about precision and timing. From this moment on, the Incapacitating Strike is yours. Use it only when the shadow is on your side.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=25
PosMap=408
DescAudio=1066
DescFinalAudio=1067

[QUEST18]
Nombre=Fumigate time
Desc=I must return to my dear Nix, but these Giant and disgusting Spiders won't let me. Can you help me? I will reward you!
DescFinal=Thanks for your help!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=15
PosMap=38
DescAudio=1068
DescFinalAudio=1069

[QUEST19]
Nombre=Low temperature
Desc=Our loggers have given us notice of the danger posed by bears roaming around Nix. It is a good opportunity to get quality leathers.
DescFinal=I thank you for the help, you can help me again with this task whenever you want.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=13
PosMap=20
DescAudio=1070
DescFinalAudio=1071

[QUEST20]
Nombre=Great mutation
Desc=So now you must go inside to finish off the Arachnid Mutant. We can't leave it there. Bring me proof that you are done with it.
DescFinal=I can't believe it, we were desperate. We believed it would be the end of our connection to Ullathorpe. This is for you.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=14
PosMap=174
DescAudio=1072
DescFinalAudio=1073

[QUEST21]
Nombre=The Guardian of the Mausoleum
Desc=It's time! Finally bring peace to all the citizens of Nix! Defeat the Mausoleum Guardian and see me again
DescFinal=You've done it! Please accept this reward.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=18
PosMap=34

[QUEST22]
Nombre=Aquatic protection
Desc=Some companions have had problems with some swimmers south of here, they are near a mysterious cave. This can't happen again, go and beat them up for me. If you have character we can keep their suits.
DescFinal=Excellent job! Have one for you, it will serve you.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=13
PosMap=106

[QUEST23]
Nombre=Arcana jewelry
Desc=Beware of these evil creatures. In the costume of one of them we find a very beautiful earring that we believe may belong to the witches who hide in our territories. Bring me as much as possible, you can quote good gold on the Ullathorpe market.
DescFinal=Thank you, this can serve you.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=20
PosMap=106

[QUEST24]
Nombre=Jabalis dependence
Desc=I have just observed along the shore that the sun is going down and we are running out of provisions for the Meson. Please go and get me ten wild boar chops!
DescFinal=I am very grateful, you have saved us. Take these coins as a reward.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=13
PosMap=55

[QUEST25]
Nombre=Some respite
Desc=Mh, I have been told about yourself, that you are good, brave, skilled and have the necessary attitude. On my part? Just words. Check it out, I need mermaid breath for an experiment. And yes, of course: there will be a prize.
DescFinal=Here is your prize
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=26

[QUEST27]
Nombre=Different types of sorcerers
Desc=If you want to learn to master magic you should start by facing those who apply it, go and go hunting inside the island. Good luck!
DescFinal=Great job, you can keep training as many times as you want.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=25

[QUEST28]
Nombre=Splinters of Blood and Wood
Desc=Listen carefully. Several maps away from Lindos lies the island of New Hope. It was once a fine place... until the ogres made it their lair. Those brutes know nothing of wood grain or craftsmanship, but the trees on that island grow nourished by a special soil. The wood absorbs the strength of the earth, and that's why their clubs don't splinter or break. I could work that wood like no one else, but I can't go looking for it alone. I need you to travel to New Hope, confront the ogres, and bring me proof that the path is clear. Kill 20 ogres and bring me 10 of their clubs. I don't care about the blood... I care about the grain. With that in my hands, Lindos will once again see works we thought were lost.
DescFinal=Well done! This is real wood. Look at these grains. Twisted, hard, full of dents... and yet they didn't break. Ogres think these clubs are only good for crushing skulls, but in the right hands they can become works worthy of Lindos.
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=25
PosMap=408

[QUEST29]
Nombre=Echoes of Ancient Antlers
Desc=Listen carefully, because I won't repeat myself. Elven wood isn't just ordinary timber. It's used to reinforce the ships of the Royal Navy and keep the kingdom's forges alive. Without it, the ports would be exposed, and enemies would soon appear. The problem is this cursed forest. My workers go in to chop it down, and they don't always return. Ancient Stags charge them without warning, tearing through armor like dry bark and leaving the camps in ruins. The Ents still watch from afar… but those stags are the forest's first warning. I need you to venture into the Elven Wood and bring them down a peg. Defeat 20 Ancient Stags and bring me 10 of their skulls. It's not cruelty: it's a message. When the forest understands that it can no longer claim the lives of Imperial workers, perhaps it will let us finish the job without further bloodshed.
DescFinal=These skulls weigh more than they look. The forest will feel their absence, I assure you. My men can now work a little more peacefully. Not safe… but alive, which is something.
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=25
PosMap=65

[QUEST30]
Nombre=Blodium's Picket Forge
Desc=You don't look like one of them. Listen, before this village froze in death, we came here for one thing: Blodium. A rare, blue mineral, as tough as the mountain itself. But it doesn't just fall to the ground. To pick it, you need a special tool, one I forged myself years ago: the Blodium Special Pickaxe. The original was lost, but I have the tools to make you a new one, if you help me clear a path so we can get out of here.
DescFinal=Perfect! With these skins I'll be able to survive the descent. Take the picket, a promise is a promise. I'm leaving now.
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=28
PosMap=182

[QUEST31]
Nombre=Coral collector
Desc=Hi, how are you? I do not do very well, since I lost mobility in the middle of the body I can no longer dive and collect corals. It was my passion and also my business, they sold very well in the port of Nix. If you are interested we could reach an agreement for money, I do not see you very capable for diving but manta rays usually eat them by mistake, you can eviscerate some of them and see if you get them.
DescFinal=We can continue to work together boy.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=25

[QUEST32]
Nombre=Fights nigromancia
Desc=The Liche is a kind of undead, the result of the transformation in which a powerful magician transforms himself through spells or rituals to achieve immortality. These dominate the first level of Marabel as a first custody of the Stone Golem that is hidden at the end protecting the sorcerers. A messenger from Ullathorpe told me that the Chief of the Guard wants us to exterminate them to leave the road to the Golem free.
DescFinal=You are amazing! The rumors about your bravery were true.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=18
PosMap=76

[QUEST33]
Nombre=Overseas robberies
Desc=I have been stripped of everything, I had a kind of deal with the pirates who frequent these coasts but they broke all the code. They used to refuel here with certain groceries at an interesting price that I found better than going to sell them in the city of Ullathorpe. Apparently a riot ensued and the captain was killed. Now someone else occupies that position. Please I need you to retrieve my cutlery, it sounds crazy I know... But they were gold!
DescFinal=I wasn't so crazy! Have you seen how precious they are?
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=27
PosMap=20
DescAudio=1088
DescFinalAudio=1089

[QUEST34]
Nombre=A stem of my size
Desc=How lucky to see you! I thought I would never see anyone around here. You're not a bandit, right? Bah, what do I say? If you were, I would already be injured. I need materials to finish building my cabin. Would you be able to bring me some wood?
DescFinal=Now if I will be able to finish my home! Thanks a lot
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=15
PosMap=271
DescAudio=1090
DescFinalAudio=1091

[QUEST36]
Nombre=North entrance
Desc=Our sentries report a large number of Bandits north of Ullathorpe; If you manage to repel their advance, I can pay you with some gold coins!
DescFinal=I congratulate you warrior, excellent work. Have this.
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=5
PosMap=5

[QUEST37]
Nombre=Ancestral magic
Desc=Within the Marabel Dungeon lies an animated entity so powerful that it owes its life to a magical component infused into it by the Witch Liches there, making it the Guardian of these infernal creatures. Our mages wish to study the enchantment that manipulates them. If you bring me a Curse Stone, you will be rewarded.
DescFinal=Excellent task! Finally our magicians will be able to explore that hidden power for so many years. Here is your reward!!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=20
PosMap=1
DescAudio=1092
DescFinalAudio=1093

[QUEST38]
Nombre=The adventure begins!
Desc=You have now reached level 13, congratulations! From now on, the adventure through the fantastic world of Argentum Online begins. My name is Heather, the person in charge of Fortune Island. Come in to receive some basic equipment... Try not to lose this so easily!
DescFinal=May luck be with you! In the Manual you will find all the answers you are looking for.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=13

[QUEST39]
Nombre=Two types of wolves
Desc=There are two types of Wolves around here, whose skins can be very useful to some Tailor in the area.
DescFinal=Well done!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=14
PosMap=1
DescAudio=1094
DescFinalAudio=1095

[QUEST40]
Nombre=Road to Ullathorpe
Desc=I need to head to the trade city, but a group of Skeleton Aggressors destroyed the path and took control of the Gulf Beaches. If you can eliminate them and allow me to travel to Ullathorpe, I'll give you a handsome reward!
DescFinal=Have this, you deserve it.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=7
PosMap=508

[QUEST41]
Nombre=Fangs of Fire
Desc=Orange snakes have begun appearing around Nix, and their venom is as fiery as their color. They're fast, aggressive, and attacking unwary travelers. Kill them before the trade route becomes impassable!
DescFinal=The citizens of Nix can rest easier knowing that this threat has been controlled, thank you adventurer.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=5
PosMap=35

[QUEST42]
Nombre=A giant problem
Desc=As if the damned snakes were not enough, another creature has appeared east of Nix, and it is truly feared. Intense magic has changed the forest bats and made them very dangerous. Help us control the threat and I will give you a treasure.
DescFinal=There is something wrong in this forest, I can sense it. I have something to ask you, talk to me again adventurer
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=8
PosMap=35

[QUEST43]
Nombre=When evil lurks
Desc=We have discovered that the force that has affected the cemetery and the Mausoleum is a damn necromancer. Help us reduce their strength, destroy their Skeleton minions and we can sleep more peacefully.
DescFinal=It can already be seen how the influence of that Necromancer is decreasing in our lands. We are deeply grateful.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=8
PosMap=35

[QUEST44]
Nombre=The Lost Embryo
Desc=Listen carefully, for I have no time for dramatics... On an island south of here, the creatures I so protected—the noble Griffons—have fallen victim to an unexpected attack. Dark, swift, and voracious lizards have invaded their nests... but that's not the worst of it! One of these vile beasts escaped with a developing embryo, the first in an ancient line... If we don't recover it, the Golden Griffon bloodline will be lost forever. Travel to the island and eliminate all the lizards you find. One of them is carrying it inside her. Yes, literally... It has swallowed it whole. You'll recognize it when you see the unusual sheen on its belly.
DescFinal=I thought I'd never see one again... The Griffon bloodline will live on thanks to you! What? You found a Mysterious Card?
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=15

[QUEST45]
Nombre=The Swamp Threat
Desc=There's no need to enter the lair. The trolls and abominations are already emerging from the swamp. Swamp Wardens patrol this edge, awaiting the order to advance. If they cross this boundary, they'll march straight to Ullathorpe. Stay outside and eliminate as many as you can. We need to keep them contained here. When you've done your part, return to me. I'll reward you with gold and experience for each threat eliminated.
DescFinal=Well done. The advance has stalled... for now. As long as we keep them out of the lair, Ullathorpe will remain safe. Take your reward. Come back if you see them regrouping.
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=18
PosMap=75

[QUEST46]
Nombre=Iron Branded by Fire
Desc=Listen carefully. The iron in these mines has always been valuable, but now it's tainted with the magic of humanoid dragons. Apparently, those creatures used it to forge weapons and perform rituals. When they awoke, the vein began to corrupt. I need you to venture into the dragon dungeon and eliminate several of those bastards. Each one that falls will weaken their influence over the mine. If we don't stop them, soon there won't be any iron left... or any miners left alive.
DescFinal=I knew it... the iron cooled again. You've severed the link between the mine and those monsters. Take this. It's not much compared to what you saved us from, but it's a fair deal.
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=20
PosMap=22

[QUEST47]
Nombre=The Purge of Marabel
Desc=Listen carefully, adventurer. These crypts were once sacred, but now they are infested with brutal orcs and liches who dabble in forbidden arts. I need you to venture into the dungeon and reduce their numbers. Every creature that falls will weaken Marabel's dark power. Return to me when your task is complete, and I will reward you with gold and experience. As long as evil persists, there will always be work for someone with courage.
DescFinal=Good work. The blood spilled today will keep Marabel under control, for now. Here is your reward. Gold and experience, just as I promised. If you still have the strength, venture back into the crypt. Evil always returns.
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=20
PosMap=70

[QUEST48]
Nombre=The Captain's Sin
Desc=Years ago, I sailed these waters believing myself immortal—not out of bravery, but out of pride. I found an ancient reliquary among stolen loot, an artifact that promised calm seas and eternal winds. I ignored the warnings, ignored my crew, and activated it. The sea responded. Not with a storm, but with damnation. My ship was split, but not sunk. My people died, but did not depart. Their souls remain bound to those galleons you see now, forced to patrol the site of my sin. They attack anything that approaches because they still obey the last order I gave: defend the loot. Go south of Nix. Look at the hull of my half-sunken vessel and sink fifteen Ghost Galleons. Each one you destroy will break a link in the chain I forged myself. I seek not forgiveness… only that my sin cease to sail.
DescFinal=The sea grows calm... for a time. I feel some voices fading, others sinking deeper. It is not redemption you bring me, captain, only silence. My sin is not washed away; it returns with the tide. And when it does, those galleons will return... as always. But as long as you continue sinking them, my dead will rest a little longer.
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=25
PosMap=211

[QUEST49]
Nombre=Science or myth?
Desc=Historians have always found that in Veril they could notice the presence of a woman with similarities to an old Greek mythology, known as Medusa. You can easily identify her by her hair, which was replaced a long time ago by snakes due to punishment; I require one of its organs to study its DNA and try to learn its darkest secrets. If you succeed, there will be a very good reward!
DescFinal=Here, you just made a great contribution to science!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=33

[QUEST50]
Nombre=The legendary
Desc=Show your worth and you will be qualified as one of the best warriors in this world. Give me both amulets, the infernal and the queen gorgon.
DescFinal=You have become one of the best fighters in this world.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=40

[QUEST51]
Nombre=Incommunicate them
Desc=In the main hall of the jellyfish cave usually appears its leader, who in turn follows the orders assigned to him by the Gorgon Queen. We need to cut that link to create chaos and leave that isolated island of reinforcements. Go and bring me proof that you have made it.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=36

[QUEST52]
Nombre=Great dragon
Desc=Come closer, noble warrior, I will tell you a story.. To the north of the Legionary Fortress, known as Arkhein, there is a lair where the most famous dragon in this world lives.. Venturing in search of it is something I do not recommend! Unless you are in physical and economic condition... You will have to show up with good equipment and a large number of potions to face this arduous task... if you do not have a Dragon Killer. You know what I mean?
DescFinal=This if it is unique, do not lose it.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=36

[QUEST53]
Nombre=Know the enemy plan
Desc=They are water monsters that have managed to evolve to the point of being able to move on land. They have admirable strength and fierce size. These monsters pose a constant threat to the City of Eldoria. We have received messages from there that have seen strange movements on the island where these creatures live. Embark there, dive into its cave and finish off the Akshas, Linns and Kadrus found there. See if you can find out anything.
DescFinal=Excellent. This is your generous pay for your services.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=33

[QUEST54]
Nombre=Unlock the tunnels
Desc=We are really worried, they are demanding more and more large quantities of iron from Banderbill for their rebuilding of the city. It would be a blessing if it weren't for how difficult it is for us to remove material from the mines. There are dark dwarfs blocking the roads and hindering our rails. Please help us with this.
DescFinal=Thank you, maybe I'll need your help again.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=25

[QUEST55]
Nombre=Resume commercial routes
Desc=To the west is a god-forsaken island. From there you access the Ruins of Earost, a mythical cave where a giant kraken lived hundreds of years ago. It has now become a pirate haven and a strategic position blocking the transportation of goods between Banderbill and Nix. I need you to head to Pirate Island, enter the cave, infiltrate them, and take down their captain. Remember to bring the rubber suit with you!
DescFinal=Thank you boy, your loyalty to the empire is priceless!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=33
DescAudio=1096
DescFinalAudio=1097

[QUEST56]
Nombre=New Minotaur Bosses
Desc=Since the arrival of the Minotaurs, iron mining has become a nightmare. We need to clear the area until we reach the depths of the Mine. If you manage to defeat the Minotaurs and bring back their horns as a sample, you will be rewarded by the guild.
DescFinal=Take these gold coins as a reward for your bravery!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=18
PosMap=369

[QUEST57]
Nombre=Pyramid III
Desc=It is impossible for me to enter the pyramid and continue my research. Can you help me?
DescFinal=Good job, here's your reward.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=19

[QUEST58]
Nombre=LEGEND ON THE KEY
Desc=Listen carefully, noble warrior: There is an ancient rumor that spiders here drop a mysterious key when they die. Can you look into it for me?
DescFinal=You've done it! With this key you can access the next level within these Catacombs. I wish you the best success in your adventure within Argentum Online, remember to always be a good person!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=15
DescAudio=1098
DescFinalAudio=1099

[QUEST59]
Nombre=Ensure the step
Desc=The only way from hell to reach the devourer of the underworld is guarded by horsemen who destroy any expedition that enters the tunnel. Although they may not seem like it, they are different from each other. Go and make your way to the end.
DescFinal=Have you managed to survive? incredible, do you think you are capable of doing it again?
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=40

[QUEST60]
Nombre=Fire magic
Desc=I need to study the magic that keeps the fire elementals alive and turns their inert mass into energy.
DescFinal=Thank you for your help, you can come back whenever you want.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=40

[QUEST61]
Nombre=Little minions
Desc=If you move a little away from the paths of the King you can find different types of caves with all kinds of creatures. I need you to find some that inhabit the surroundings of Marabel. The citizens of Banderbill fear because these little goblins perform minor magic activities with voodoo dolls, it really is not a big problem but you would help me reassure the population if you bring some of them to prove their ineffectiveness.
DescFinal=Have these coins, thank you for your bravery.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=13
DescAudio=1100
DescFinalAudio=1101

[QUEST62]
Nombre=Exploring the swamp
Desc=To the north is the Swamp, one of the most dangerous areas around our beloved Ullathorpe. You must help us clear the area to prevent these creatures from causing chaos in our commercial city.
DescFinal=Great job! Wait! Don't go, there is still work to do..
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=18

[QUEST63]
Nombre=Plag of creatures
Desc=I never thought that living so close to the desert would turn into this drama. I have already tried everything possible to keep these creatures from coming near my cabin, but to no avail. Can you help me get out?
DescFinal=I will always remember your name!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=13
PosMap=82
DescAudio=1102
DescFinalAudio=1103

[QUEST64]
Nombre=Forestry
Desc=Don't be scared with me, I won't hurt you. Have you never seen someone with a green complexion? We are not many orcs here on the mainland but there is always a first time. I liked this location to build my house, it guarantees me some security to be close to the city of the King, but the tigers that lurk around here do not understand laws. If you clear the area a little and get the Scroll, I will give you a reward that will help you, you don't look very agile...
DescFinal=This is luxurious for me. Have what was promised.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=20
PosMap=194

[QUEST65]
Nombre=Brute force
Desc=I don't know what you do here, it's not a place to wander. You look very cunning and capable, but from afar I can notice that your arms lack vigor. We can come to an agreement to offer you that bit that is missing in you. As you could see in the surroundings there are several bears. I alone cannot guarantee the safety of the area, help me by defeating several bears, if you get the Scroll of Strength, you will receive a brutal reward!
DescFinal=Good job, this will be of great help for your training.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=18
PosMap=25

[QUEST66]
Nombre=Legionary Shield
Desc=Legionario, ho osservato i tuoi sforzi in nome della Legione Oscura. Non tutti possiedono la disciplina e la forza d'animo necessarie per portare i nostri emblemi, ma tu potresti essere l'eccezione. Se riuscirai a raccogliere 10 Distintivi Rossi, trofei conquistati in combattimento, torna da me. In cambio, ti concederò uno Scudo della Legione, forgiato per coloro che hanno dimostrato vera lealtà e resilienza. Ricorda, questo onore non è per tutti. Solo Cacciatori, Lavoratori, Bardi, Assassini e Banditi possono aspirare a portare questo simbolo della nostra forza. Vai, legionario. Dimostra di esserne degno.
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=23
PosMap=295
DescAudio=1104

[QUEST68]
Nombre=Royal Shield
Desc=Soldier, your service to the Royal Navy has not gone unnoticed. Discipline and honor are the pillars that sustain us... and you have shown yourself to understand their value. Gather 10 Blue Badges and report to me. In return, you will be awarded a Navy Shield, worthy of those who protect order and the crown. This recognition is reserved only for Warriors, Workers, Paladins, and Clerics serving in the Navy. Fulfill your duty, and you will be rewarded accordingly.
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=23
PosMap=294

[QUEST69]
Nombre=Real avant -garde shield
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=43

[QUEST70]
Nombre=White horse
Desc=Do you need something faster than my brother's Brown Horse? If you manage to get 1 White Horse Horseshoe for me, I can give you my horse in exchange to improve your transportation. Do not take this mission unless you are prepared to complete it. If you abandon this mission, you risk losing your current mount.
DescFinal=You can now equip my White Horse! When you are stronger, visit my brother Marcelo, maybe he will have a better gift for you!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=28

[QUEST71]
Nombre=Armored brown horse
Desc=Do you need something faster than my brother's Mule? If you manage to get 1 Brown Horse Horseshoe for me, I can give you my horse in exchange to improve your transportation. Do not take this mission unless you are prepared to complete it. If you abandon this mission, you risk losing your current mount.
DescFinal=Now you can ride my Brown Horse! When you are stronger, visit my brother Cristian, maybe he will have a better gift for you!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=24

[QUEST72]
Nombre=Fighter's mount
Desc=Do you need something faster than my brother's White Horse? If you manage to get 1 Fighter's Horseshoe for me, I can give you my horse in exchange to improve your transportation. Do not take this mission unless you are prepared to complete it. If you abandon this mission, you risk losing your current mount.
DescFinal=Now you can ride my Mount! When you are stronger, visit my brother Guido, maybe he will have a better gift for you!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=32

[QUEST74]
Nombre=Troll terror
Desc=Those damned Dark Trolls will pay for all the fear they have instilled in our City; If you kill 5 of them you will get a big reward.
DescFinal=Excellent work! Have this, you will always be welcome here.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=19

[QUEST75]
Nombre=Legendary weapons chest
Desc=A weapon of the highest level for badges.
DescFinal=Good luck.
