[QUEST310]
Nombre=Sétimo presente de Natal
Desc=As event participants contribute Christmas Cookies to this city's community counter, this Christmas's rewards will be unlocked. To receive this Christmas Gift, you must have a Christmas Star in your inventory and wait until the community has contributed a total of 350,000 Christmas Cookies.
Repetible=1

