[NPC1018]
Name=Arkan <Quest>
Desc=Hey... watch your step, stranger. Do you see the horizon to the south? The sea isn't empty... it's hungry. And those galleons won't rest until they've collected their debt.
Body=284
Head=38
NpcType=17
DisabledInBattleServer=1

[NPC1019]
Name=Tharzug <Quest>
Desc=You feel the call, but it is still weak. The goblins listen, the dead obey... the orcs resist. If you desire their strength, you must break their spirit. Return when the war spirits recognize you.
Body=558
Head=311
NpcType=17

[NPC1020]
Name=Morgrath <Quest>
Desc=It's not often someone finds my cabin and lives to tell the tale. I see the trace of necromancy in your hands... Summoning Zombies, isn't it? That spell is crude, unstable. I can refine it... transform it into something more useful.
Body=666
Head=424
NpcType=17

[NPC1021]
Name=Eldren <Quest>
Desc=The panthers of the forest have grown more aggressive. They have blocked the path to Penthar, and my magic is no longer enough to keep them at bay. However... I sense within you the echo of the Wild Roar. Perhaps, with the right test, I could teach you to make it resonate more powerfully.
Body=157
Head=109
NpcType=17

[NPC1022]
