Body=272
Head=21
NpcType=17

[NPC1023]
Name=Sahret <Quest>
Desc=The sea carries ancient echoes... and you are no stranger to them. I live here, between the shore and the sand, watching the pyramid for more years than I can count. If you have come to this house, it is because the Arcane Roar now answers your voice.
