Desc=Greetings, adventurer. Not many approach me without seeking weapons or potions, but I pursue something different: knowledge. In the depths of the Catacombs dwell fascinating creatures: spiders imbued with the power of the elements. Their silk contains fragments of that primal energy. I have dedicated years to studying how to transform them into a unique material, but gathering them is far too perilous a task for a mere scholar.
